Package: openfhe
Title: R Interface to the OpenFHE Fully Homomorphic Encryption Library
Version: 1.1.5-1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Balasubramanian", "Narasimhan", email = "naras@stanford.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5852-7639"))
  )
Description: Provides an R interface to the OpenFHE C++ library for fully
    homomorphic encryption (FHE). Supports BFV, BGV, and CKKS schemes for
    computation on encrypted data, as well as FHEW/TFHE for Boolean circuit
    evaluation. Designed as a production-grade upgrade path from the
    'homomorpheR' package.
License: BSD_2_clause + file LICENSE
